    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed per scoping agreement consistent with MRL 2 requirements. CFD predictions of relative hemolysis index are within 9% of experimental bench measurements across all five operating points, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. The evidence package is judged sufficient to support the regulatory claim that the CFD model correctly identifies worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
